{"tid":961390,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"全家都話我垃圾","createTime":"2018-12-30T05:43:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-30T10:44:31.000Z","uid":137967,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b22b11071d92a813427ef5b9cb7cca62ae0ea85e","tid":961390,"uid":137967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T05:43:27.000Z","msg":"［member]依幾日老母叫我帶佢個大陸嚟香港玩嘅契女行下街，佢話覺得我地年紀差唔多，一定有計傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n琴晚翻到屋企，我同老母呻下，行街嗰陣好攰好尷尬<br />\n點知佢屌翻我，細佬將我po ig呻嘅post全部俾晒老母睇<br />\n就咁同老豆老母嘈起上嚟，我落左街自己喊<br />\n頭先細佬大大聲同屋企人投訴我，話我嘈到夜晚一點幾，阻住佢訓，搞到佢三點幾先訓得著，佢第二日要温書<br />\n明明十二點幾我就走左，都唔明點解佢要屈我<br />\n最開心嘅係全家從來冇問過我感受，只會叫我從佢地角度出發。 就算細佬態度幾差，都會氹佢<br />\n我就嚟受唔住，好想離開咁嘅世界。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> [/member]"},{"pid":"f904a7084b4ea12a79cc4609ad9c129ebf1d6056","tid":961390,"uid":177089,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T05:45:21.000Z","msg":"member<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"682b725934d1059248e8f8bc07f68b7a1ae5b325","tid":961390,"uid":137967,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f904a7084b4ea12a79cc4609ad9c129ebf1d6056","tid":961390,"uid":177089,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T05:45:21.000Z","msg":"member<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T05:46:05.000Z","msg":"㩒錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac0ded2ae553ed27db8e43fb03871b8dca837260","tid":961390,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"682b725934d1059248e8f8bc07f68b7a1ae5b325","tid":961390,"uid":137967,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f904a7084b4ea12a79cc4609ad9c129ebf1d6056","tid":961390,"uid":177089,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T05:45:21.000Z","msg":"member<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-3